msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node. The quantized model `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3"
" (64G × 16)."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode。量化模型 `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` 可部署在 1 个 Atlas 800 "
"A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"- Setting the environment variable `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` enables balance scheduling. This may help increase output throughput and reduce TPOT in v1 scheduler. However, TTFT may degrade in some scenarios. Furthermore, enabling this feature is not recommended in scenarios where PD is separated.\n"
"- For single-node deployment, we recommend using `dp4 tp4` instead of `dp2 tp8`.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length - that is, the sum of input and output tokens for a single request. For performance testing with an input length of 3.5K and output length of 1.5K, a value of `16384` is sufficient, however, for precision testing, please set it at least `35000`.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. To enable it, remove this option.\n"
"- `--mm-encoder-tp-mode` indicates how to optimize multi-modal encoder inference using tensor parallelism (TP). If you want to test the multimodal inputs, we recommend using `data`.\n"
"- If you use the w4a8 weight, more memory will be allocated to kvcache, and you can try to increase system throughput to achieve greater throughput."
msgstr ""
"- 设置环境变量 `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING=1` 可启用均衡调度。这有助于在 v1 调度器中提高输出吞吐量并降低 TPOT。但在某些场景下，TTFT 可能会变差。此外，不建议在 PD 分离的场景中启用此功能。\n"
"- 对于单节点部署，建议使用 `dp4 tp4` 而非 `dp2 tp8`。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出 token 之和。对于输入长度 3.5K、输出长度 1.5K 的性能测试，`16384` 的值已足够；但对于精度测试，请至少设置为 `35000`。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` 表示禁用前缀缓存。如需启用，请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--mm-encoder-tp-mode` 指示如何使用张量并行（TP）优化多模态编码器推理。如果要测试多模态输入，建议使用 `data`。\n"
"- 如果使用 w4a8 权重，将为 kvcache 分配更多内存，可以尝试提高系统吞吐量以获得更大的吞吐。"

msgid ""
"The service returns HTTP 200 OK with a JSON response containing the "
"`choices` field. Example output:"
msgstr "服务返回 HTTP 200 OK，JSON 响应中包含 `choices` 字段。示例输出："

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-Node Data Parallel Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.2 多节点数据并行部署"

msgid ""
"`Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` can be deployed across multiple nodes using data "
"parallelism. This deployment mode requires at least 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)"
" nodes."
msgstr ""
"`Kimi-K2.5-w4a8` 可以使用数据并行跨多个节点部署。此部署模式至少需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点。"

msgid "Run the following scripts on two nodes respectively."
msgstr "分别在两个节点上运行以下脚本。"

msgid "=== \"Node 0\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 0\""

msgid "=== \"Node 1\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 1\""

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-size`: total number of data parallel ranks across all nodes. In this example, `4` means the model is split across 4 DP ranks total (2 per node).\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local`: number of data parallel ranks running on the current node. In this example, each node runs 2 DP ranks.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank`: starting rank offset for data parallel ranks on this node. Node 0 starts at rank 0 (default), Node 1 starts at rank 2. This ensures each node's DP ranks occupy distinct positions in the overall rank space.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address`: IP address of the data parallel master node (Node 0). This value must be consistent with `local_ip` set on Node 0.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port`: RPC port for data parallel master communication. Must be the same across all nodes.\n"
"- `--headless`: indicates that this vLLM instance is not the master service node. Only set on non-master nodes (Node 1). The master node (Node 0) should NOT set this flag.\n"
"- For single-node deployment, we recommend using `dp4 tp4` instead of `dp2 tp8`."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-size`：所有节点上数据并行秩的总数。在此示例中，`4` 表示模型总共分布在 4 个 DP 秩上（每个节点 2 个）。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local`：当前节点上运行的数据并行秩数量。在此示例中，每个节点运行 2 个 DP 秩。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank`：当前节点上数据并行秩的起始秩偏移量。节点 0 从秩 0 开始（默认），节点 1 从秩 2 开始。这确保每个节点的 DP 秩在整体秩空间中占据不同的位置。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address`：数据并行主节点（节点 0）的 IP 地址。此值必须与节点 0 上设置的 `local_ip` 一致。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port`：数据并行主节点通信的 RPC 端口。所有节点必须相同。\n"
"- `--headless`：表示此 vLLM 实例不是主服务节点。仅在非主节点（节点 1）上设置。主节点（节点 0）不应设置此标志。\n"
"- 对于单节点部署，我们建议使用 `dp4 tp4` 而不是 `dp2 tp8`。"

