msgid "### 5.3 Multi-Node PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.3 多节点 PD 分离部署"

msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment: "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"我们建议使用 Mooncake "
"进行部署：[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid ""
"In the standard single-node deployment mode, Prefill (prompt processing) and"
" Decode (token generation) tasks run on the same set of NPUs. PD (Prefill-"
"Decode) separation addresses this by running Prefill and Decode on dedicated"
" node groups, each configured independently:"
msgstr ""
"在标准单节点部署模式下，Prefill（提示处理）和 Decode（令牌生成）任务在同一组 NPU 上运行。PD（Prefill-"
"Decode）分离通过将 Prefill 和 Decode 运行在专用的节点组上来解决此问题，每个节点组独立配置："

msgid ""
"- **Prefill nodes** focus on high-throughput prompt processing, optimized for compute and communication (e.g., enabling FlashComm for Allreduce acceleration).\n"
"- **Decode nodes** focus on low-latency token generation, optimized for memory bandwidth (e.g., enabling MLAPO fusion operators)."
msgstr ""
"- **Prefill 节点**专注于高吞吐量的提示处理，针对计算和通信进行了优化（例如，启用 FlashComm 以加速 Allreduce）。\n"
"- **Decode 节点**专注于低延迟的令牌生成，针对内存带宽进行了优化（例如，启用 MLAPO 融合算子）。"

msgid ""
"This architecture is recommended for production deployments with concurrent "
"multi-user workloads, where stable latency and high throughput are both "
"required."
msgstr "对于需要同时保证稳定延迟和高吞吐量的并发多用户工作负载的生产部署，建议采用此架构。"

msgid ""
"Take Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) for example, we recommend to deploy 2P1D (4 "
"nodes) rather than 1P1D (2 nodes), because there is not enough NPU memory to"
" serve high concurrency in 1P1D case."
msgstr ""
"以 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 为例，我们建议部署 2P1D（4 个节点）而不是 1P1D（2 个节点），因为在 1P1D "
"情况下没有足够的 NPU 内存来服务高并发。"

msgid "- `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8 2P1D`: requires 4 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) nodes."
msgstr "- `Kimi-K2.5-w4a8 2P1D`：需要 4 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 节点。"

msgid ""
"To run the vllm-ascend `Prefill-Decode Disaggregation` service, you need to "
"deploy a `launch_online_dp.py` script and a `run_dp_template.sh` script on "
"each node and deploy a `proxy.sh` script on prefill master node to forward "
"requests."
msgstr ""
"要运行 vllm-ascend `Prefill-Decode 分离`服务，您需要在每个节点上部署 `launch_online_dp.py` 脚本和 "
"`run_dp_template.sh` 脚本，并在 prefill 主节点上部署 `proxy.sh` 脚本以转发请求。"

msgid "Parameter descriptions:"
msgstr "参数说明："

msgid ""
"|Parameter|Type|Required|Default|Description|\n"
"|---------|----|--------|-------|-----------|\n"
"|`--dp-size`|int|Yes|-|Data parallel size (total number of DP ranks across all nodes).|\n"
"|`--tp-size`|int|No|1|Tensor parallel size within each DP rank.|\n"
"|`--dp-size-local`|int|No|(same as `--dp-size`)|Number of DP ranks on the current node. If not set, defaults to `--dp-size`.|\n"
"|`--dp-rank-start`|int|No|0|Starting rank offset for data parallel ranks on this node.|\n"
"|`--dp-address`|str|Yes|-|IP address of the data parallel master node (node 0).|\n"
"|`--dp-rpc-port`|str|No|12345|RPC port for data parallel master communication.|\n"
"|`--vllm-start-port`|int|No|9000|Starting port for each vLLM engine instance on this node. Each DP rank's engine port = `vllm_start_port` + local rank index.|"
msgstr ""
"|参数|类型|必需|默认值|描述|\n"
"|---------|----|--------|-------|-----------|\n"
"|`--dp-size`|int|是|-|数据并行大小（所有节点上的 DP 秩总数）。|\n"
"|`--tp-size`|int|否|1|每个 DP 秩内的张量并行大小。|\n"
"|`--dp-size-local`|int|否|（与 `--dp-size` 相同）|当前节点上的 DP 秩数。如果未设置，则默认为 `--dp-size`。|\n"
"|`--dp-rank-start`|int|否|0|此节点上数据并行秩的起始秩偏移量。|\n"
"|`--dp-address`|str|是|-|数据并行主节点（节点 0）的 IP 地址。|\n"
"|`--dp-rpc-port`|str|否|12345|数据并行主节点通信的 RPC 端口。|\n"
"|`--vllm-start-port`|int|否|9000|此节点上每个 vLLM 引擎实例的起始端口。每个 DP 秩的引擎端口 = `vllm_start_port` + 本地秩索引。|"

msgid "1. `run_dp_template.sh` script"
msgstr "1. `run_dp_template.sh` 脚本"

msgid "=== \"Node 0(Prefill)\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 0(Prefill)\""

msgid "=== \"Node 1(Prefill)\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 1(Prefill)\""

msgid "=== \"Node 0(Decode)\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 0(Decode)\""

msgid "=== \"Node 1(Decode)\""
msgstr "=== \"节点 1(Decode)\""

msgid ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`: enables the communication optimization function on the prefill nodes.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MLAPO=1`: enables the fusion operator, which can significantly improve performance but consumes more NPU memory. In the Prefill-Decode (PD) separation scenario, enable MLAPO only on decode nodes.\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable: true`: enables the recomputation scheduler. When the Key-Value Cache (KV Cache) of the decode node is insufficient, requests will be sent to the prefill node to recompute the KV Cache. In the PD separation scenario, it is recommended to enable this configuration on both prefill and decode nodes simultaneously.\n"
"- `multistream_overlap_shared_expert: true`: When the Tensor Parallelism (TP) size is 1 or `enable_shared_expert_dp: true`, an additional stream is enabled to overlap the computation process of shared experts for improved efficiency."
msgstr ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`：在 prefill 节点上启用通信优化功能。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MLAPO=1`：启用融合算子，可以显著提升性能但会消耗更多 NPU 内存。在 Prefill-Decode (PD) 分离场景下，仅在 decode 节点上启用 MLAPO。\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable: true`：启用重计算调度器。当 decode 节点的键值缓存（KV Cache）不足时，请求将被发送到 prefill 节点以重新计算 KV Cache。在 PD 分离场景下，建议同时在 prefill 和 decode 节点上启用此配置。\n"
"- `multistream_overlap_shared_expert: true`：当张量并行（TP）大小为 1 或 `enable_shared_expert_dp: true` 时，启用额外的流以重叠共享专家的计算过程，从而提高效率。"

msgid ""
"The `run_dp_template.sh` scripts use positional parameters (`$1`-`$7`) to "
"receive configuration values from `launch_online_dp.py`:"
msgstr ""
"`run_dp_template.sh` 脚本使用位置参数（`$1`-`$7`）从 `launch_online_dp.py` 接收配置值："

msgid ""
"- `$1` (`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`): the NPU devices assigned to this DP instance, e.g., `0,1,2,3` or `4,5,6,7`.\n"
"- `$2` (`--port`): the vLLM server port for this DP instance, auto-assigned starting from `--vllm-start-port` (e.g., `7100`, `7101`).\n"
"- `$3` (`--data-parallel-size`): total number of DP ranks.\n"
"- `$4` (`--data-parallel-rank`): the rank index of this DP instance.\n"
"- `$5` (`--data-parallel-address`): IP address of the DP master node.\n"
"- `$6` (`--data-parallel-rpc-port`): RPC port for DP master communication.\n"
"- `$7` (`--tensor-parallel-size`): TP size within each DP rank."
msgstr ""
"- `$1` (`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`)：分配给此 DP 实例的 NPU 设备，例如 `0,1,2,3` 或 `4,5,6,7`。\n"
"- `$2` (`--port`)：此 DP 实例的 vLLM 服务器端口，从 `--vllm-start-port` 开始自动分配（例如 `7100`、`7101`）。\n"
"- `$3` (`--data-parallel-size`)：DP 秩的总数。\n"
"- `$4` (`--data-parallel-rank`)：此 DP 实例的秩索引。\n"
"- `$5` (`--data-parallel-address`)：DP 主节点的 IP 地址。\n"
"- `$6` (`--data-parallel-rpc-port`)：DP 主节点通信的 RPC 端口。\n"
"- `$7` (`--tensor-parallel-size`)：每个 DP 秩内的 TP 大小。"

