msgstr "PD分离服务完全启动后，通过预填充主节点上的代理端口发送请求，验证预填充节点和解码节点是否协同正常工作："

msgid ""
"The proxy returns HTTP 200 OK. The JSON response contains the `choices` "
"field with the generated text, confirming that Prefill nodes have "
"successfully processed the prompt and Decode nodes have generated the "
