msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, "
"precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> "
"**注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求和部署机器比例等因素。建议根据实际情况参考第9.2节进行调优。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes. 1 "
"node = 1 Atlas 800 A3 server (64G × 16 NPUs)."
msgstr "> `*NPU总数`表示所有节点使用的NPU总数。1个节点 = 1台Atlas 800 A3服务器（64G × 16 NPU）。"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Deployment Mode|*Total NPUs|Weight Version|Key Considerations|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput / Low Latency<br>(16K context)|Single-Node Mixed|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|Use dp4 tp4 for optimal throughput and low latency|\n"
"|High Throughput / Low Latency<br>(16K context)|2-Node Data Parallel|16 (A2)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|dp4 tp4 across 2 nodes; balanced latency and throughput|\n"
"|High Throughput / Low Latency<br>(16K context)|2P2D deployment|64 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|Prefill: dp2 tp8; Decode: dp32 tp1 for high concurrency|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, low concurrency ≤4)|Single-Node Mixed|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|dp1 tp16 to maximize TP, accommodate extreme context lengths|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, high concurrency >4)|Single-Node Mixed|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|dp2 tp8 to optimize memory bandwidth and support higher concurrency|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|部署模式|*NPU总数|权重版本|关键考量|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐量/低延迟<br>(16K上下文)|单节点混合|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|使用dp4 tp4以获得最佳吞吐量和低延迟|\n"
"|高吞吐量/低延迟<br>(16K上下文)|2节点数据并行|16 (A2)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|跨2个节点的dp4 tp4；平衡延迟和吞吐量|\n"
"|高吞吐量/低延迟<br>(16K上下文)|2P2D部署|64 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|预填充：dp2 tp8；解码：dp32 tp1以实现高并发|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，低并发≤4)|单节点混合|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|dp1 tp16以最大化TP，适应极端上下文长度|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，高并发>4)|单节点混合|16 (A3)|kimi-k2.5-w4a8|dp2 tp8以优化内存带宽并支持更高并发|"

